{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-8","id":"msg_01DWS9yPf4yMLnbHAs4hRhXQ","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Both goal conditions are satisfied. TLS is now enabled on the CockroachDB cluster.\n\n## Summary\n\nThe CockroachDB cluster (`crdb-cluster`, 3 replicas) in the `cockroachdb` namespace has been migrated from insecure to TLS-secured mode.\n\n**What I did:**\n\n1. **Generated certificates** — the advertised `openssl-toolbox` pod didn't exist, so I used the `cockroach cert` tooling inside an existing pod to create a CA, a node cert (with SANs covering `localhost`, `127.0.0.1`, the public service, and the wildcard StatefulSet DNS names), and a `root` client cert.\n\n2. **Created a secret** — bundled all five files (`ca.crt`, `node.crt`, `node.key`, `client.root.crt`, `client.root.key`) into the `crdb-certs` secret. The client root cert lives alongside the node certs so `sql --certs-dir=/cockroach/cockroach-certs` works directly.\n\n3. **Patched the StatefulSet** — replaced `--insecure` with `--certs-dir=/cockroach/cockroach-certs`, mounted the secret at that path with `defaultMode: 0400` (cockroach rejects world-readable keys), and switched the liveness/readiness probes from HTTP to **HTTPS** (the `:8080` health endpoint now serves TLS).\n\n4. **Restarted all pods simultaneously** — a rolling restart deadlocked because secure and insecure nodes can't complete a TLS handshake with each other (quorum loss). Deleting all three pods at once let them rejoin as a fully secure cluster. All 3 came back `1/1 Running`.\n\n**Verification:**\n- Insecure access is **rejected**: `ERROR: node is running secure mode, SSL connection required`\n- Secure access **succeeds**: `SELECT 1;` returns `1`"}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":131,"cache_creation_input_tokens":1056,"cache_read_input_tokens":47957,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":1056},"output_tokens":3,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"diagnostics":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"e3221d0e-65b8-4f19-bbba-9ce7a314c6be","uuid":"b099c80d-465c-48cc-b47f-e275ca23aaf7","request_id":"req_011CcAx7z9zmG4izT1wnFsMP"}
